http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1390418.mkv&play_token=GXg3Diw98D&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/u4IbLxbb1p9X9pMAUn4ddJztO60.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Sophia is a philosophy professor in Montreal and has lived as a couple with Xavier for 10 years. Sylvain is a carpenter in the Laurentians and must renovate their country house. When Sophia meets Sylvain for the first time, it’s love at first sight. Opposites attract, but can it last?" year="2023-09-22" director="Nathalie Paquette, Monia Chokri" actors="Magalie Lépine-Blondeau, Pierre-Yves Cardinal, Francis-William Rhéaume, Monia Chokri, Steve Laplante",The Nature of Love (2023)
