#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/kgUk1wti2cvrptIgUz0VTAtSF6w.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Adèle's life is changed when she meets Emma, a young woman with blue hair, who will allow her to discover desire, to assert herself as a woman and as an adult. In front of others, Adele grows, seeks herself, loses herself, finds herself." year="2013-10-09" director="Frédéric Alexandre, Bahijja El Amrani, Antoine Fromental, Monya Galbi, Auriane Lacince" actors="Léa Seydoux, Adèle Exarchopoulos, Salim Kéchiouche, Aurélien Recoing, Catherine Salée",Blue Is the Warmest Color (2013)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1289066.mkv&play_token=MbMO4Qot8K&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/xO9h6o4LGagbnvwql41hL9tBcrm.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="1916. Julien Delaunay is reported missing in action during the Great War. His wife, Julie, refuses to believe he is dead. 1919. When a photo of an amnesic drifter appears in the press, Julie immediately recognizes him as her beloved husband. They are reunited and, little by little, she helps him to fall in love with her again. Until another woman claims to be the man’s real wife…" year="2023-04-05" director="Guillaume Bureau, Joseph Bellot, Judith Dozières" actors="Louise Bourgoin, Leïla Bekhti, Karim Leklou, Jean-Charles Clichet, Ghislain de Fonclare",Loving Memories (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1289053.mkv&play_token=S3A1sKrFBt&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/11CkMVD0dPjhAZPaf0u9VfS46lw.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="A man tries to make his wife fall in love with him again, after waking up in an alternate reality where she never knew him." year="2019-01-18" director="Matthieu de la Mortière, Lisa-Nina Rives, Hugo Gélin" actors="François Civil, Joséphine Japy, Benjamin Lavernhe, Camille Lellouche, Amaury de Crayencour",Love at Second Sight (2019)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1289076.mkv&play_token=Zf3UcVA1m3&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/vBOioZKaGacNtx8G7qZeTPqemk7.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Diane is a well-known lawyer, divorced for three years. She loses her mobile telephone and receives a call from the person who finds it. That person is Alexandre, a charming man and the perfect gentleman. They make a connection over the phone and agree to meet up the following day. But when Alexandre arrives, there's a surprise in store when Diane discovers he is only 4' 6' tall. From that moment on, Diane tries to overcome the prejudices of society and her own fears to experience the best time of her life..." year="2016-05-04" director="Laurent Tirard" actors="Jean Dujardin, Virginie Efira, Cédric Kahn, César Domboy, Stéphanie Papanian",Up for Love (2016)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1289090.mkv&play_token=ZCRhFPaoqo&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/tFuMLNU3IeWvNMaasJwsDkqbR3T.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="A la fin des années soixante, deux familles émigrent en Israël et se retrouvent voisines dans un minuscule village perdu au milieu de nulle part. L'une vient du Maroc et l'autre de l'Inde. Hormis un rêve, ces gens n'ont rien en commun.  Loin de leurs habitudes et de leurs influences culturelles, ils tentent de reconstruire leur monde. Obligées de cohabiter, les deux communautés se jaugent et tentent d'exister par ce qui les différencie. De malentendus en préjugés, la route vers l'harmonie s'annonce aussi tortueuse que surprenante." year="2004-06-06" director="Avi Nesher" actors="Liraz Charhi, Netta Garti, Jean Benguigui, Parmeet Sethi, Krutika Desai Khan, Ruby Porat Shoval, Nati Ravitz, Aure Atika, Rotem Abuhab, Israel Katorza",FR - Au bout du monde à gauche (2004)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1276511.mp4&play_token=lZqq10tN6N&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/7InKwVFgvIgfwuPKd0C3R9OeoN7.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="As a patriarchal family yearns for the birth of a son to continue their family line, their youngest son secretly joins an erotic dance theatre and falls for its transgender starlet." year="2022-11-18" director="Saim Sadiq, Sana Jafri, Hyra Basit, Qasim Abbas, Tashish Habib" actors="Ali Junejo, Rasti Farooq, Alina Khan, Sarwat Gilani, Salmaan Peerzada",Joyland (2022)
