#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/koswMk0y7jGcyofV1sBccnNtY0B.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Mira Ray, dealing with the loss of her fiancé, John, sends a series of romantic texts to his old cell phone number… not realizing the number was reassigned to Rob Burns' new work phone. Rob, a journalist, is captivated by the honesty in the beautifully confessional texts. When he’s assigned to write a profile of megastar Céline Dion, he enlists her help in figuring out how to meet Mira in person and win her heart." year="2023-05-04" director="Mark Cockren, Cordelia Hardy, Thom McNally, Suzanne McGeachan, Jim Strouse" actors="Priyanka Chopra Jonas, Sam Heughan, Céline Dion, Sofia Barclay, Russell Tovey",Love Again (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1216083.mkv&play_token=3h1jGlIQEQ&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/xxu4Z5lYY22k5mQNS7Uh9ihR9rU.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Nora et Léo se rencontrent le jour de la rentrée en classe de Seconde. Leur regard s’enchâssent et tout est dit. Nora vit dans l’ensemble HLM de la Ville, Léo dans le quartier résidentiel. Le frère de Nora, Tarek, travaille comme manutentionnaire à l’hypermaché local. Accusé de vol, il clame son innocence, mais le directeur du magasin ne veut rien entendre et le vire sur le champ. Le directeur, c’est Franck, le père de Léo. Les deux familles s’affrontent, les différences s’exacerbent et le chaos s’installe. Les vies de Nora et Léo s’embrasent et virent à la tragédie…" year="2023-01-04" director="Philippe Lioret" actors="Sabrina Levoye, Teïlo Azaïs, Jean-Pierre Lorit, Marie Dompnier, Ferjria Deliba, Arsène Mosca, Nassim Lyes, Myriem Akheddiou, Iliana Khelif, Nicolas Grandhomme",FR - 16 ans (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1203495.mkv&play_token=q8OoSgOQxw&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/2dlftyPz7mTYbrsPvTogyFmYd7d.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="It's the battle of wills, as Andie needs to prove she can dump a guy in 10 days, whereas Ben needs to prove he can win a girl in 10 days. Now, the clock is ticking—and the wildly entertaining comedy smash is off and running in this irresistible tale of sex, lies and outrageous romantic fireworks!" year="2003-02-07" director="Donald Petrie, Ellen H. Schwartz, Stuart Feldman, Grant Lucibello, Jack Gill" actors="Kate Hudson, Matthew McConaughey, Kathryn Hahn, Annie Parisse, Adam Goldberg",How to Lose a Guy in 10 Days (2003)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1201277.mkv&play_token=Mg0QuXUBaI&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/p4RafgAPk558muOjnBMHhMArjS2.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Cal Weaver is living the American dream. He has a good job, a beautiful house, great children and a beautiful wife, named Emily. Cal's seemingly perfect life unravels, however, when he learns that Emily has been unfaithful and wants a divorce. Over 40 and suddenly single, Cal is adrift in the fickle world of dating. Enter, Jacob Palmer, a self-styled player who takes Cal under his wing and teaches him how to be a hit with the ladies." year="2011-07-29" director="Glenn Ficarra, John Requa, Jayne-Ann Tenggren" actors="Steve Carell, Ryan Gosling, Julianne Moore, Emma Stone, Lio Tipton",Crazy - Stupid - Love. (2011)
