#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/yqd1CmwaXQkLXVLsO2cqiExplb1.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Sons of Caribbean immigrants, Francis and Michael face questions of masculinity, identity and family amid the pulsing beat of Toronto's early hip-hop scene. A mystery unfolds when escalating tensions set off a series of events which changes the course of the brothers’ lives forever." year="2023-03-17" director="Clement Virgo, Jenny Mac, Claire Bonduro, Alan McKenna" actors="Lamar Johnson, Aaron Pierre, Kiana Madeira, Marsha Stephanie Blake, Lovell Adams-Gray",Brother (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1189137.mkv&play_token=8tof06tpku&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/jBAYPL15J3BecGujAydLZ1a06mF.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="This comical love story follows the story of A.J. Fikry, whose life is not at all what he expected it to be. His wife has died, his bookstore is experiencing the worst sales in its history and now his prized possession, a rare edition of Poe poems, has been stolen. He’s given up on people and even the books in his store offer another reminder that the world is changing too rapidly. But when a mysterious package arrives at the store, it gives Fikry the chance to make his life over and see things anew." year="2022-10-07" director="Hans Canosa, Conrad de la Torres III, Roger Mendoza" actors="Kunal Nayyar, Lucy Hale, Christina Hendricks, David Arquette, Scott Foley",The Storied Life of A.J. Fikry (2022)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1188851.mkv&play_token=7ttNFaTQ2B&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

